{"tid":23115,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍長拖 分手係點行翻出嚟","createTime":"2016-12-04T18:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T04:12:59.000Z","uid":22790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2db2367e8946ffc269792cfba61dbbfdcdc43284","tid":23115,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:08:00.000Z","msg":"點樣可以行翻出黎 我戴左帽都仲幫佢諗藉口 好想佢翻轉頭 我好冇用<br />\n四年半喇 到底點樣放低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點再信下一個人 <br />\n佢變左生命一部分 點樣去適應一個新既人<br />\n要重新去接納其他人 所有事重新開始<br />\n所以計劃既野都係假 下一次又會唔會發生同樣既事<br />\n每行過一段路 生活每一件小事 都有你既影子<br />\n每年既重要日子都一齊過 我可以點面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619b85dfa9cb3a2a98ce92c749f9e4981ef76386","tid":23115,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:13:49.000Z","msg":"冇人拍長拖分手？ 都好既至少大家都好幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52267c3bc8075cff6a1e109bd37b7d18e54a2ca3","tid":23115,"uid":20998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:15:37.000Z","msg":"我都行唔到出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0726e83aff84ed48436b19d7465fa531ea190743","tid":23115,"uid":2548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:16:11.000Z","msg":"你幾歲？"},{"pid":"0445f26aa820d097033007010d8467270964b9aa","tid":23115,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:16:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都行唔到出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打一齊左幾耐 因咩事分手<img src=\"/assets/faces