d":"70184722d457b39d3d2c1218128914b0e9e4dbe4","tid":23115,"uid":34148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:21:19.000Z","msg":"拍左八年散左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝佢幸福快樂囉，唔係點"},{"pid":"e8af8c88bd28628fedf51f3dd98690f09e8b39d8","tid":23115,"uid":20998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:23:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實放低一個人好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同人講咪易囉 到自己發生左先知有幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nI know that feel bro"},{"pid":"eaa3ee63b3c689a2d60a7c6a127c131273b60572","tid":23115,"uid":21558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:23:17.000Z","msg":"我男朋友對上一個又係拍左四年<br />\n佢聲稱自己用左差不多四年去平復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話自己每日都行屍走肉<br />\n逼自己去忙<br />\n之後就識左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f68529bcba9b9e1f60f074baed30fb0b5d8cfd","tid":23115,"uid":48687,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:23:25.000Z","msg":"五年<br />\n分手後sad左三年<br />\n日日都好唔慣<br />\n睇住佢期間換左幾個 更加心痛<br />\n<br />\n直到再拍返拖 發現原來可以開心過以前<br />\n<br />\n雖然以前係刻骨銘心<br />\n分開左好似無左忽肉咁<br />\n每朝起身又好唔慣 有種失落感<br />\n但諗返起 如果無經歷呢5年<br />\n我唔會遇到依加呢個<br />\n當初根本無需要咁傷心同令身邊既人擔心<br />\n<br />\n係你既就係你<br />\n唔係就諗幾多都無用"},{"pid":"b1a25022a08876c496d04c16dcd8fcab24526f28","tid":23115,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:24:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當你搵到下一個就會慢慢走返出嚟<br />\n但真係未必投入到 相處間好多之前嘅影子<br />\n呢家都煩緊點算<br />\n<br />\n利申：拍左六年散左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n六年好長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實好怕會搵左水泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5c375368961c8656d047387dac763106344ff5","tid":23115,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:25:41.000Z","msg":"琴日散左 拍左四年<br />\n覺佢有好多好多野對唔住佢<br />\n佢終於下定決心放棄我<br />\n<br />\n但我仲係好愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131ac5a5e8ca6e23a1ce17b9627822c0e1c8759b","tid":23115,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>時間會沖淡一切 我之前兩年感情<br />\n一開頭唔慣完之後過一個月已經無乜所謂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n或者其實係你冇想象中咁愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85159d4878eea408b3508e8ac7225acdbba654f9","tid":23115,"uid":28376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:25:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>時間會解決問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n時間好折磨人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係折磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n折磨到下一個出現<br />\n回想返就會覺得點解個陣要咁唔開心"},{"pid":"73d5bde29f85ce0eb16a1ca80e61153f15feeb1a","tid":23115,"uid":55679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:25:55.000Z","msg":"識過第二個"},{"pid":"ca1e9b17c997c14c46f2cbba52f15eef67c62681","tid":23115,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:26:01.000Z","msg":"一齊左4年11個月<br />\nCome on james...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日諗起佢 但可能只係唔慣...<br />\n好似係..."},{"pid":"9b4d988339f40ba8c1110e7814e29e614b0fe75f","tid":23115,"uid":7168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:26:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一齊左4年11個月<br />\nCome on james...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日諗起佢 但可能只係唔慣...<br />\n好似係...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n散左兩個月"},{"pid":"c24e5157c8370c011d18bc2a950afc8bf4732dfe","tid":23115,"uid":2102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-