lockquote><blockquote>經驗講比我聽千祈唔好同返前度一齊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為只會傷得更深"},{"pid":"1aaff7b130588657ec988d039f3d44d96812d8b4","tid":23115,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:28:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我男朋友對上一個又係拍左四年<br />\n佢聲稱自己用左差不多四年去平復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話自己每日都行屍走肉<br />\n逼自己去忙<br />\n之後就識左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢宜家有你好幸福啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011da3bcfb0343bba0a91982405ec2a176325fbc","tid":23115,"uid":2102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:29:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>經驗講比我聽千祈唔好同返前度一齊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n變左心唔會再返黎架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你八年因咩分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"b2411aa77561b36cc739d8a62fd6f2c19a86aff6","tid":23115,"uid":4100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:29:29.000Z","msg":"忙下分下心<br />\n頭幾個月係好難捱架啦 最好就掉曬啲有關佢既野"},{"pid":"688320bd7840fdfa93f14bac340641f868d16c12","tid":23115,"uid":25790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:29:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當你搵到下一個就會慢慢走返出嚟<br />\n但真係未必投入到 相處間好多之前嘅影子<br />\n呢家都煩緊點算<br />\n<br />\n利申：拍左六年散左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n六年好長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實好怕會搵左水泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寧缺莫濫 不過如果年紀大開始急就難搞啲<br />\n<br />\n其實未走得返出嚟就開始 對新一任都好唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e7cad031ba6eb02211040dcbd48432139f7afaa","tid":23115,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:30:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>五年<br />\n分手後sad左三年<br />\n日日都好唔慣<br />\n睇住佢期間換左幾個 更加心痛<br />\n<br />\n直到再拍返拖 發現原來可以開心過以前<br />\n<br />\n雖然以前係刻骨銘心<br />\n分開左好似無左忽肉咁<br />\n每朝起身又好唔慣 有種失落感<br />\n但諗返起 如果無經歷呢5年<br />\n我唔會遇到依加呢個<br />\n當初根本無需要咁傷心同令身邊既人擔心<br />\n<br />\n係你既就係你<br />\n唔係就諗幾多都無用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明日後會有更好既出現 但你sad個三年係點捱過去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98eb294dbe3f6cffa4a07af46d8959f31293efc9","tid":23115,"uid":34148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:31:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拍左八年散左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝佢幸福快樂囉，唔係點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n八年 點解可以咁灑脫 我自問做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n留又留過，戴帽個時又係我原諒佢，又好似你咁幫佢搵埋藉口，到頭來一句價值觀唔同，8年感情都無情講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我無奈多於唔開心，之後終於明，感情係薄過紙。"},{"pid":"f68b6371b1ac2a1e6776f830de7c6be252249bad","tid":23115,"uid":40148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:31:06.000Z","msg":"我都係啱啱分手冇耐 一齊左3年 真係好難適應冇左佢係度既感覺"},{"pid":"110fdf0d940359e44716cab616d374ed11e6a43f","tid":23115,"uid":4058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:31:43.000Z","msg":"睇透呢個世界冇所謂真愛一生一世就得"},{"pid":"d3f6e6ae9b2e46aa8f3123142636c2ad50dd0080","tid":23115,"uid":21558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:32:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我男朋友對上一個又係拍左四年<br />\n佢聲稱自己用左差不多四年去平復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢話自己每日都行屍走肉<br />\n逼自己去忙<br />\n之後就識左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢宜家有你好幸福啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n錯啦，我成日諗<br />\n既然一個男人可以為一個女人傷心四年，其實呢個前度係佢心入面係咪冇人取代到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢屋企電腦前仲放住前度送既擺件<br />\n我有問過，佢話冇特別意義<br />\n不過我最近發現佢掉左<br />\n可能我太冇安全感，我覺得我係水泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c58978892e358a646992da1e49c87c4261e02401","tid":23115,"uid":22790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:32:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一齊左4年11個月<br />\nCome on james...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日諗起佢 但可能只係唔慣...<br />\n好似係...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n散左兩個月</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以前拍拖試過嘈分手拖拉左一個月 最後終於分手 我傷心左一日 <br />\n今次我就明自己真係唔係唔慣 係我聽係中意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89e19fa2d04d655679bc0435482d17ec7cc9c08","tid":23115,"uid":2102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:32:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇透呢個世界冇所謂真愛一生一世就得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n看透左就連拖都唔想拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590ab181b34e109e482611223516f73ca8d6841d","tid":23115,"uid":34148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:34:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>經驗講比我聽千祈唔好同返前度一齊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n變左心唔會再返黎架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你八年因咩分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n性格不合，價值觀唔同......喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原因都係藉口俾佢自己好過啲啫，不愛就是不愛了......"},{"pid":"4